<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.9">
<l>vaṉpēy mulaiyuṇ ṭatōrvā yuṭaiyaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">vaṉtū ṇeṉaniṉ ṟatōrvaṉ parattai</l>
<l>taṉpē riṭṭukkoṇṭu taraṇi taṉṉil</l>
<l rend="indent">tāmō taraṉtāṅ kutaṭa varaitāṉ</l>
<l>muṉpē vaḻikāṭ ṭamucuk kaṇaṅkaḷ</l>
<l rend="indent">mutukil peytutam muṭaikkuṭ ṭaṉkaḷai</l>
<l>kompēṟ ṟiyirun tukuti payiṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉumkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great mountain that,</l>
<l rend="indent">having been given His name,</l>
<l>was borne upon the earth by Damodara</l>
<l rend="indent">—he with the mouth that ate [from] the breast of the mighty demoness—</l>
<l rend="indent">standing like a strong pillar bearing a heavy burden,</l>
<l>called Govardhana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where monkey troops teach their young,</l>
<l rend="indent">having been placed on [their] backs,</l>
<l rend="indent">to leap and reach for branches while showing the way forward,</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
